Package com.niklasarndt.healthchecksio.model

This package contains model classes for (De)Serialization (JSON Data to Java Objects or reverse).

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Check
    The model class Check represents a status check, identified by a UUID (write access) or unique key (read-only).
    Integration
    The model class Integer represents a notification channel (only available with full api key).
    Ping
    The model class Ping represents a single message to the api (only available with full api access).
    StatusFlip
    The model class StatusFlip represents a status change (check went up or down).

Package com.niklasarndt.healthchecksio.model Description

This package contains model classes for (De)Serialization (JSON Data to Java Objects or reverse).

For more information on the models, visit the wiki.
